<normalizedToken id="E828C44852BC1EDA55B00EABCEB17DEB" originalValue="Catolés">Catoles</normalizedToken>
; vertical seep on rock; 26.ii.2018; leg. Benetti &amp; team; BR18-0226-01C&quot; (INPA). 
<emphasis id="8F5ED0829523FBA95191A4A7B67365C3" bold="true" pageId="18" pageNumber="127">Paratypes (15): BRAZIL: Bahia</emphasis>
